OL,6,FEmergency crews, including the Wales
OL,7,FAir Ambulance, were called to the
OL,8,Fplant; however, Mr Day was pronounced
OL,9,Fdead at the scene.
OL,11,FAt a hearing, a barrister representing
OL,12,Fthe Health and Safety Executive told a
OL,13,Fcourt how Mr Day had been servicing a
OL,14,Fcoil tilter machine at the plant.
OL,16,FThe machinery, used to transport large
OL,17,Fsteel coils away from the hot mill,
OL,18,Fwas operated via electric laser beams
OL,19,Fand was known to workers at the plant
OL,20,Fas the hot cross bun.
