OL,6,FWhile working on the coil tilter, the
OL,7,Fmachinery was isolated and turned off
OL,8,Fto ensure a safe working environment.
OL,10,FAfter completing the job and signing
OL,11,Foff the relevant paperwork, the court
OL,12,Fwas told Mr Day was called back to the
OL,13,Fplant due to an oil leak which was
OL,14,Fdiscovered in the coil tilter machine.
