OL,6,FMr Day entered the area with the
OL,7,Fmachinery, but was unaware that the
OL,8,Fequipment had been turned back on and
OL,9,Fwas live. CCTV footage played to the
OL,10,Fcourt showed Mr Day's movements
OL,11,Factivating the coil tilter, leading to
OL,12,Fhim being fatally crushed.
