OL,6,FGiving evidence, Tata Steel Mechanical
OL,7,FInspector Ben Cooper, who was working
OL,8,Fon the leak at the time of the
OL,9,Fincident, told the court how he had
OL,10,Ftried to contact Mr Day on a radio
OL,11,Fseveral times to bring tools, but was
OL,12,Funable to make contact.
OL,14,FAnother engineer answered the call,
OL,15,Fand Mr Cooper said he didn't see the
OL,16,Fneed to stand down Mr Day as he had
OL,17,Fnot answered his radio.
OL,19,FJustin Day's wife, Zoe Day, told ITV
OL,20,FNews her life changed forever the day
OL,21,Fher husband died.
