OL,6,F"It was the worst day of my life and
OL,7,Fmy children's lives," she said.
OL,9,F"You can't even imagine or put into
OL,10,Fwords how you feel. Your world just
OL,11,Fcomes crashing down, and you don't
OL,12,Fgather the thoughts in your head. I
OL,13,Fjust remember the house being so full
OL,14,Fof people and thinking this doesn't
OL,15,Fseem real."
OL,17,F"We relive this every single day, you
OL,18,Fcan't get on with your life. He's
OL,19,Fmissed so much", Zoe said.
