OL,6,F"I'm not the same person I was; I
OL,7,Fnever will be. We had such a beautiful
OL,8,Ffamily."
OL,10,F"He was just an amazing man, an
OL,11,Famazing father. I met him when I was
OL,12,F16, so I had 24 years with him,
OL,13,Fthankfully. Life will never be the
OL,14,Fsame."
